		<item>
		<title>那几种水果治便秘（这种水果号称“便秘克星”！）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/7958.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 21 Jul 2023 07:01:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[山药]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[火龙果]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=7958</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[水果山药球 推荐月龄：8M+ 配餐用途：配餐 功效：防便秘/健脾养胃/锻炼咀嚼 营养特点 火龙果最大的特点是含 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/95a4e7ca6f28547e11d18a7349bc4fe0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">水果山药球 推荐月龄：8M+</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">配餐用途：配餐</p>功效：防便秘/健脾养胃/锻炼咀嚼
                
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">营养特点</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">火龙果最大的特点是含有丰富的膳食纤维和植物性白蛋白。膳食纤维可以促进肠道蠕动，具有很好的通便作用。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">可贵的是这种白蛋白，它会自动与人体内的重金属离子结合 ，通过排泄系统排出体外，从而起到解毒作用。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">宝宝吃火龙果的时候，一不小心就弄得满身都是果汁。今天这道山药球，把水果和山药结合在一起，吃起来软糯，没有多余汁水，还可以健脾养胃哦。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">食材工具</span></strong></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/9e15b4cac69e41ceca6c147ef3d16cf3.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">准备食材：椰蓉：适量，</span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">芒果：30克，</span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">火龙果：30克，猕猴桃：30克，铁棍山药：270克</span></span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">工具：蒸锅、碾压棒</span></span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e86a37b331663b96ee19bd5dae75e960.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">1.山药去皮切段，放入蒸锅蒸20分钟，碾压成泥。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">»山药容易引起过敏，处理的时候建议戴上手套 。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/7b72ae75ae720994a4c28a7384b7e10b.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">2.火龙果、芒果、猕猴桃，去皮后切丁。山药分成三份，分别加入三种水果，碾压均匀。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">»如果宝宝咀嚼能力不佳，我们可以把火龙果和猕猴桃的籽过滤掉。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/75a026232b33739b2ed1fcffccb0d6d1.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">3.取适量山药泥，搓成圆球状。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">»山药球的大小可以根据宝宝的抓握能力而定。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/3e233bc7c9e5343e42edecaa34574226.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">4.搓完的山药球，表面撒上椰蓉。椰蓉可以丰富口感和防粘。</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/09be13d311d812889e852c1c3a385755.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">5.这样就完成了，水果味浓郁，口感软糯还能健脾养胃~</span></span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/22691d532ccbddb9b0938482abeb91de.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">添加要领</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">●椰蓉也可以用奶粉、米粉、熟糯米粉代替。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">●山药的粘液不用完全清洗干净，它有增强免疫力的作用。</span></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">●里面的水果可以根据自家喜好去替换，尽量选择水分少的。</span></span></p>


